stration and API group configuration\n3. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go**: Package documentation and kubebuilder markers\n4. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go**: DeepCopy methods for all types\n5. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go**: Comprehensive unit tests (32 test cases)\n6. **config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml**: CRD YAML definition\n7. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md**: Package documentation and usage examples\n\n### Test Coverage\n\nAll 32 unit tests pass, covering:\n- Type metadata and API group version\n- Spec structure and default values\n- Status conditions\n- List type operations\n- JSON serialization/deserialization\n- Scheme registration\n- All sandbox configuration types (containers, volumes, probes, affinity, tolerations, security contexts)\n- DeepCopy functionality\n\n### API Contract\n\nThe implementation follows the delta-spec exactly:\n- API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- Version: `v1alpha1`\n- Kind: `AgentRuntime`\n- Resource Plural: `agentruntimes`\n- Short Names: `ar`, `agentruntime`\n- Status Subresource: Enabled\n- Printer Columns: Age\n- Default Values: SessionTimeout=15m, MaxSessionDuration=8h\n\n### Notes\n\nAll requirements from the delta-spec have been implemented:\n- ✓ Type metadata reflects GVR mapping\n- ✓ Resource plural matches client-go expectations\n- ✓ Spec structure with required fields\n- ✓ Duration fields use metav1 types\n- ✓ Status with conditions support\n- ✓ List type for collection operations\n- ✓ Scheme registration for serialization\n- ✓ CRD subresources support (status)\n- ✓ Default values for spec fields\n- ✓ OpenAPI validation markers\n- ✓ Print columns for kubectl readability\n- ✓ JSON tag naming convention (camelCase)\n- ✓ DeepCopy methods for safety\n- ✓ Validation markers for fields\n- ✓ Label selector support\n- ✓ Watch support (via client-go)","additions":59,"deletions":6},"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan