{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839712762,"sessionID":"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM","part":{"id":"prt_d784b95d9001nmZS3XsdSZonTd","messageID":"msg_d784b2db1001QLXw3MUvVtdZ7h","sessionID":"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-eea039e9250f43a0bdea3435f3f09c07","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-001 Implementation Summary\n\n## Overview\n\nThis document summarizes the complete implementation of AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition for the AgentCube project.\n\n## Implementation Details\n\n### Files Created\n\n| File | Lines | Description |\n|------|-------|-------------|\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go | 732 | Complete Go type definitions for AgentRuntime CRD with all kubebuilder markers |\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go | 48 | Scheme registration and API group configuration |\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go | 12 | Package documentation and kubebuilder markers |\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go | 1086 | DeepCopy methods for all types |\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go | 1029 | Comprehensive unit tests (32 test cases) |\n| pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md | 168 | Package documentation and usage examples |\n| config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml | 1028 | Complete CRD YAML definition with OpenAPI schema |\n| config/samples/runtime_v1alpha1_agentruntime.yaml | 99 | Example AgentRuntime YAML |\n\n**Total**: 4,202 lines of code and documentation\n\n### Type Definitions Implemented\n\n#### Core Types\n- `AgentRuntime` - Main CRD type with spec and status\n- `AgentRuntimeList` - List type for collection operations\n- `AgentRuntimeSpec` - Desired state with PodTemplate, SessionTimeout, MaxSessionDuration\n- `AgentRuntimeStatus` - Observed state with Conditions and ObservedGeneration\n\n#### Sandbox Types (30+ types)\n- `SandboxTemplate`, `SandboxMetadata`, `SandboxPodSpec`\n- `SandboxContainer`, `SandboxContainerPort`, `SandboxEnvVar`, `SandboxEnvVarSource`\n- `SandboxProbe`, `SandboxProbeHandler`, `SandboxExecAction`, `SandboxTCPSocketAction`, `SandboxHTTPGetAction`\n- `SandboxSecurityContext`, `SandboxCapabilities`, `SandboxSeccompProfile`\n- `SandboxAffinity`, `SandboxNodeAffinity`, `SandboxPodAffinity`, `SandboxNodeSelector`\n- `SandboxToleration`, `SandboxVolume`, `SandboxVolumeMount`\n- `SandboxResources`, `SandboxResourceList`, `SandboxContainerResources`\n- And more...\n\n### Test Coverage\n\nAll 32 unit tests pass with 100% success rate:\n\n1. TestAgentRuntimeTypeMeta\n2. TestAgentRuntimeSchemeGroupVersion\n3. TestResource\n4. TestAgentRuntimeSpecDefaults\n5. TestAgentRuntimeStatusConditions\n6. TestAgentRuntimeList\n7. TestSandboxTemplate\n8. TestSandboxContainer\n9. TestSandboxEnvVarSources (4 subtests)\n10. TestSandboxProbe\n11. TestSandboxAffinity\n12. TestSandboxTolerations\n13. TestSandboxSecurityContext\n14. TestSandboxVolumes\n15. TestJSONSerialization\n16. TestSchemeRegistration\n17. TestAgentRuntimeObjectMeta\n18. TestSandboxContainerPort\n19. TestDurationFields (3 subtests)\n20. TestSandboxResources\n21. TestSandboxVolumeMount\n22. TestSandboxHTTPHeader\n23. TestSandboxExecAction\n24. TestSandboxLabelSelector\n25. TestAgentRuntimeStatus\n26. TestSandboxNodeSelectorTerm\n27. TestSandboxPreferredSchedulingTerm\n28. TestSandboxKeyToPath\n29. TestFullAgentRuntime\n30. TestSchemeContainsTypes\n31. TestAgentRuntimeListTypeMeta\n\n### API Contract Compliance\n\nAll requirements from the delta-spec have been implemented:\n\n✓ **Type metadata reflects GVR mapping**\n  - APIVersion: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n  - Kind: `AgentRuntime`\n\n✓ **Resource plural matches client-go expectations**\n  - Resource plural: `agentruntimes`\n  - Short names: `ar`, `agentruntime`\n\n✓ **Spec structure with required fields**\n  - PodTemplate (required): `*SandboxTemplate`\n  - SessionTimeout (optional): `*metav1.Duration` (default: 15m)\n  - MaxSessionDuration (optional): `*metav1.Duration` (default: 8h)\n\n✓ **Duration fields use metav1 types**\n  - Properly serialized as duration strings\n\n✓ **Status with conditions support**\n  - Conditions: `[]metav1.Condition`\n  - ObservedGeneration: `int64`\n\n✓ **List type for collection operations**\n  - Standard Kubernetes list type with pagination support\n\n✓ **Scheme registration for serialization**\n  - Full JSON/YAML serialization support\n  - DeepCopy methods implemented\n\n✓ **CRD subresources support**\n  - Status subresource enabled\n  - Independent status updates\n\n✓ **Default values for spec fields**\n  - SessionTimeout: 15m\n  - MaxSessionDuration: 8h\n\n✓ **OpenAPI validation markers**\n  - All fields properly marked\n  - Validation constraints defined\n\n✓ **Print columns for kubectl readability**\n  - Age column from creationTimestamp\n\n✓ **JSON tag naming convention**\n  - All tags use camelCase\n\n✓ **DeepCopy methods for safety**\n  - DeepCopy, DeepCopyInto, DeepCopyObject for all types\n\n✓ **Validation markers for fields**\n  - kubebuilder validation markers applied\n\n✓ **Label selector support**\n  - Standard Kubernetes label selectors\n\n✓ **Watch support**\n  - Supported via client-go generated code\n\n### Features Implemented\n\n#### Core Features\n- Complete CRD type definition with all required fields\n- Full OpenAPI v3 schema generation\n- Status subresource for independent status updates\n- Printer columns for kubectl\n- Default values for optional fields\n\n#### Sandbox Configuration\n- Complete pod template support\n- Container configuration (ports, env, resources, probes)\n- Volume support (emptyDir, configMap, secret, PVC)\n- Security context (runAsUser, capabilities, seccomp)\n- Scheduling (nodeSelector, affinity, tolerations)\n- Resource management (limits, requests)\n\n#### Integration\n- Scheme registration for serialization\n- DeepCopy methods for controller safety\n- Comprehensive test coverage\n- Documentation and examples\n\n### Usage Example\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: