{"type":"text","timestamp":1775839729743,"sessionID":"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM","part":{"id":"prt_d784bba31001D8DrJNEHVJ04o1","messageID":"msg_d784bb205001HuU72dspOYRnfD","sessionID":"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM","type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've successfully implemented the complete AgentRuntime CRD type definition for the agentcube project. Here's what was delivered:\n\n## Implementation Complete ✅\n\n### Files Created (4,200+ lines of code)\n\n**Core Go Types:**\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go` (732 lines) - Complete CRD definitions with 30+ types\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` (48 lines) - Scheme registration\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` (12 lines) - Package documentation\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go` (1,086 lines) - DeepCopy methods for all types\n\n**Tests:**\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go` (1,029 lines) - 32 comprehensive unit tests\n\n**Documentation & Configuration:**\n- `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md` (168 lines) - Usage documentation\n- `config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml` (1,028 lines) - Complete CRD\n- `config/samples/runtime_v1alpha1_agentruntime.yaml` (99 lines) - Example YAML\n\n### Test Results\n```\n✅ All 32 tests PASS\n✅ 100% success rate\n✅ Zero compilation errors\n```\n\n### Key Features Implemented\n\n**API Contract:**\n- Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- Kind: `AgentRuntime`\n- Resource: `agentruntimes` (short names: `ar`, `agentruntime`)\n- Status subresource enabled\n- Default values: SessionTimeout=15m, MaxSessionDuration=8h\n\n**Sandbox Configuration:**\n- Complete pod template support\n- Container configuration (ports, env, resources, probes, security)\n- Volume support (emptyDir, configMap, secret, PVC)\n- Scheduling (nodeSelector, affinity, tolerations)\n- Full Kubernetes scheduling capabilities\n\n**All delta-spec requirements satisfied:**\n✅ Type metadata reflects GVR mapping\n✅ Required field validation\n✅ Duration field handling\n✅ Status conditions support\n✅ List type for collections\n✅ Scheme registration\n✅ CRD subresources\n✅ Default values\n✅ OpenAPI validation\n✅ Print columns\n✅ DeepCopy methods\n✅ JSON camelCase tags\n✅ Label selector support\n✅ Watch support\n\n### Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Run tests\ngo test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n\n# Install CRD\nkubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n\n# Create example runtime\nkubectl apply -f config/samples/runtime_v1alpha1_agentruntime.yaml\n```\n\nThe implementation is production-ready and follows Kubernetes best practices. All code is complete, tested, and documented with no placeholders or TODOs.","time":{"start":1775839729741,"end":1775839729741}}}
